							Para cualquier información no dude en ponerse en contacto con nosotros. Le responderemos a la 
							mayor brevedad posible.							
						</p>
					</div><!--/.section-header-->
					<div class="contact-content">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
								<div class="single-contact-box">
									<div class="contact-right">
										<div class="contact-adress">
											<div class="contact-office-address">
												<h3>Información de contacto</h3>
												<p>
													<a style="color: white;" href="https://goo.gl/maps/EH9wrpnbWQgQFM2V9">Pez, 23 (Madrid)</a>
																								
												</p>
												<div class="contact-online-address">
													<div style="color: white;" class="single-online-address">
														<i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
														<a style="color: white;"href="tel: 34677360757"><span>+34 677 36 07 57</span></a>														
														
													</div><!--/.single-online-address-->
													
													<div class="single-online-address">
														<i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i>
														<a style="color: white;"href="mailto: margotpereira@hotmail.com"><span>margotpereira@hotmail.com</span></a>														
													</div><!--/.single-online-address-->
												</div><!--/.contact-online-address-->
											</div><!--/.contact-office-address-->
											<div class="contact-office-address">
												<h3>Redes sociales</h3>
												<div class="contact-icon">
													<ul>
														<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/javier.serrano.3760"><i class="fa fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><!--/li-->
														<li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-google-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li><!--/li-->
